{"tid":1660273,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 中国人於台灣政大貼連儂牆鬧笑話 推爆佢","createTime":"2019-10-17T12:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T14:21:06.000Z","uid":311962,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2af43ffefaad14ee964c2ef6ebf96df70ad61c0b","tid":1660273,"uid":311962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"台灣台北市政治大學遭到中国人張貼低能文宣<br />\n被台灣學生反將一軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經原作者同意轉貼自PTT文章<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1571300669.A.576.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1571300669.A.576.html&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=48b6c1a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1571300669.A.576.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1571308337.A.97A.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1571308337.A.97A.html&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=1882826c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1571308337.A.97A.html</a><br />\n<br />\n事情是這樣的<br />\n在最近許多連儂牆的衝突中<br />\n我們似乎非常和平<br />\n頂多只有一名小粉紅在活動鬧場罷了<br />\n但今天終於有位勇敢的中國學生挑戰了<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gRctAIn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgRctAIn.jpg&h=cddebc99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然是很刺眼<br />\n不過我們是文明人，立刻盛大歡迎他享受民主，享受言論自由<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VH5PeIx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVH5PeIx.jpg&h=6c3e4118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lD2IkRL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlD2IkRL.jpg&h=1f9dc495&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UNgzsNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUNgzsNE.jpg&h=54d07214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RmFKiBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRmFKiBA.jpg&h=072b106b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WGmJiis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWGmJiis.jpg&h=65c8bb9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望他接受到言論自由的美妙了&hearts; &hearts; &hearts;<br />\n<br />\n更新<br />\n上完課又多了一些東西 <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AuMeJrc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAuMeJrc.jpg&h=678c619e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dx5VTgL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fdx5VTgL.jpg&h=05cf0bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n毛James東 <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vAquK1W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvAquK1W.jpg&h=d8d8be66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NWA4a3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNWA4a3a.jpg&h=62718cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/flcZAk2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FflcZAk2.jpg&h=d72a540d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rwDpOkF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrwDpOkF.jpg&h=c5b3b4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/E2rDftQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FE2rDftQ.jpg&h=7ee24ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒經費就送你一點 <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5fmi0A6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5fmi0A6.jpg&h=64b8ca0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三語言聲明 <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6riiH5W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6riiH5W.jpg&h=3bf1ef77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習特勒 <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yok3KZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fyok3KZM.jpg&h=2c4ba97e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這就是言論自由 希望同胞能理解 總有一天光復我大中華！<br />\n<br />\n最新情況<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2WJNak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2WJNak.jpg&h=d23c3b92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f722520628b4e8d29a3e345eb9bb987fa1cabdd1","tid":1660273,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"281665277a86733558bf00a3114f7d979ac83f8b","tid":1660273,"uid":183834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGHEkwR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGHEkwR.jpg&h=d996a09b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d30145ff316e67c8a9da748c672e7c8a93e5c0e","tid":1660273,"uid":318091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:07:17.000Z","msg":"好正啊<br />\n<br />\n希望唔好俾人清"},{"pid":"9575e4411601bd63dc6090c8737ee7ed328ac21c","tid":1660273,"uid":323443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"台港同盟！"},{"pid":"bebb93f6f6a4c38c93dc5022a57ffe5b09d55f79","tid":1660273,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8e4706e64db9998177b12b3370623452fa02c6","tid